White Rabbit 

The hospital is quarantined after it's inundated with the victims of a mysterious and deadly plague, which spreads to the hospital staff. A five year old girl can't be found as she chases the pet rabbit of the first plague victim throughout the hospital. A man with a tree limb through his chest has to be admitted to the ER despite the quarantine if he is to live.
